data.title: Flock of A**holes
data.meta_description: Flock of A**holes is a Local Rock, Hair Metal Cover Band from Worcester, Massachusetts.
data.text:
About

We are Worcester's favorite 80's cover band playing you all the hits. The winner's of several awards for best cover band in Worcester. Many years in a row!!! We play at the "Luckydog Music Hall", 89 Green st in Worcester, one weekend show per month, our home base!!!....We are always interested in taking your requests to play weddings, private functions, etc. So please feel free to ask....
